OL,3,CSchoolgirl's murderer fails in his
OL,4,Cattempt to overturn conviction
OL,6,FThe man convicted of the murder of
OL,7,Fschoolgirl Nikki Allan has failed in
OL,8,Fhis bid to appeal his conviction and
OL,9,Fsentence.
OL,11,FNikki was killed in October 1992 and
OL,12,Fher murder went unsolved for more than
OL,13,F30 years until a DNA breakthrough
OL,14,Fenabled detectives to link 57-year-old
OL,15,FDavid Boyd to the crime.
OL,17,FBoyd from Stockton was found guilty of
OL,18,Fbeating seven-year-old Nikki with a
OL,19,Fbrick and stabbing her 37 times in a
OL,20,Fdisused building near her home in
OL,21,FSunderland.
