OL,6,FHe was jailed for life in May last
OL,7,Fyear and told he would serve a minimum
OL,8,Fof 29 years in prison for her murder.
OL,10,FWatch a special report from Gregg
OL,11,FEasteal from May 2023 when Boyd was
OL,12,Fconvicted.
OL,14,FNearly 5 months on from his
OL,15,Fsentencing, Boyd lodged an appeal for
OL,16,Fhis conviction in September 2023.
