OL,3,CSchoolgirl's murderer fails in his
OL,4,Cattempt to overturn conviction
OL,6,FToday (4 October 2024) it was revealed
OL,7,Fthat his application was recently
OL,8,Fthrown out by the Court of Appeal,
OL,9,Fmeaning Boyd's original sentence will
OL,10,Fstill stand.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "This case did
OL,13,Fnot proceed to the full court."
OL,15,FHe will continue to serve his life
OL,16,Fsentence where he will serve a minimum
OL,17,Fof 29 years behind bars.
