OL,6,FDuring the murder trial judge heard in
OL,7,FMay 2023, Mrs Justice Lambert told
OL,8,FBoyd: "You decided to kill her, to
OL,9,Fsilence her and prevent her from
OL,10,Ftelling anyone that you had sexually
OL,11,Fassaulted her or attempted to do so.
OL,12,FIt would not have taken the seven-year-
OL,13,Fold long to appreciate she was trapped
OL,14,Fin that cold and dark building and
OL,15,Fthat you were coming through the
OL,16,Fwindow to get her.
